Welcome to Hattira!
You can see it live here - http://hattira.herokuapp.com

- Setup -
* sudo npm install
* bower install
* grunt
* install mongo and start by "mongod"
* http://localhost:3000/


- Tests -
* Run all tests using 'npm test'


* Tests for Client side code written in Angular JS
** Tests are written in Jasmine and Karma is used as a Test runner
** To run tests ' ./node_modules/karma/bin/karma start'
